[Psalms 78:25](../../../bib/kjv/psa078.htm#025.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_025">psa 78:25</span></span>

angels' food--literally, "bread of the mighty" (compare [Psa
105:40](../../../bib/kjv/psa105.htm#040).md); so called, as it came from
