[Psalms 78:51](../../../bib/kjv/psa078.htm#051.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_051">psa 78:51</span></span>

chief of their strength--literally, "first-fruits," or, "first-born"
([Gen 49:3](../../../bib/kjv/gen049.htm#003.md); [Deu
21:17](../../../bib/kjv/deu021.htm#017).md).

