[Exo 15:1](../../../bib/kjv/exo015.htm#001).md).

[Psalms 78:54](../../../bib/kjv/psa078.htm#054.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_054">psa 78:54</span></span>

border of his sanctuary--or, "holy border"--i. e., region of which--

this mountain--(Zion) was, as the seat of civil and religious
